race.comment: Looks a race with a stack of chances. EPIC PROPORTIONS (1) got the chocolates at Doomben last time out and winning jockey Fenlon stays on board. Again gets the benefit of her 2kg claim and is drawn to get the run of the race from the inside marble. Rates the testing material. BOOMTOWN BOSS (2) wasn't disgraced in Group 3 level before the spell and will find this task a bunch easier. Gets the services of Maloney in the saddle and a strong showing while fresh is on the cards. STREET CHASE (6) has a solid record at this circuit with a win and two seconds from just four starts. In the mix if he brings his A-game. TOWN CRIER (7) is a two-time winner over this track and trip and is usually thereabouts. One of the main contenders.
